{"kanda":6,"sarga":110,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तौतथायुध्यमानौतुसमरेरामरावणौ ।ददृशुस्सर्वभूतानिविस्मितेनान्तरात्मना","trans":"As Rama and Ravana were thus fighting in war, all beings watched with astonishment in mind.","words":[{"d":"समरे","m":"in war"},{"d":"तथा","m":"thus"},{"d":"युध्यमनौ","m":"fighting"},{"d":"रामरावणौ","m":"Rama and Ravana"},{"d":"सर्वभूतानि","m":"all beings"},{"d":"विस्मितेन","m":"with astonishment"},{"d":"अन्तरात्मना","m":"in mind"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"observed"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"अर्धयन्तौतुसमरेतयोस्तौस्यन्दनोत्तमौ ।परस्परमभिक्रुद्धौपरस्परमभिद्रुतौ","trans":"Both of them were moving quickly seeking to gain one another, very furiously persevering.","words":[{"d":"तयोः","m":"both"},{"d":"स्यन्दनोत्तमौ","m":"both moving quickly"},{"d":"परस्परम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"अर्धयन्तौ","m":"seeking to gain"},{"d":"अभिक्रुद्धौ","m":"very furious"},{"d":"परस्परम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"अभिद्रुतौ","m":"persevering"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"परस्परवधेयुक्तौघोररूपौबभूवतुः ।मण्डलानि च वीधीश्चगतप्रत्यागतानि च दर्शयन्तौबहुविधांसूतसामर्थ्यजांगतिम् ।","trans":"Both striking one another diligently, going in circles moving forward and backward displaying feats, went on.","words":[{"d":"परस्परवधे","m":"striking one another"},{"d":"युक्तौ","m":"diligently"},{"d":"मण्डलानि","m":"in circles"},{"d":"वीधीश्च","m":"feats"},{"d":"गतप्रत्यागतानि","m":"forwarding and receding"},{"d":"सूतसामर्थ्यजाम्","m":"displaying charioteers skills"},{"d":"बभूवतुः","m":"went on"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"अर्धयन्रावणंरामोराघवंचापिरावणः गतिवेगंसमापन्नौप्रतिवेगप्रवर्तने ।","trans":"Ravana hurting Rama and vice versa displaying quickness in retaliation and speed of arrows, the fight happened.","words":[{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"अर्धयन्","m":"hurting"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"रावणःचापि","m":"hurting Ravana"},{"d":"प्रतिवेगप्रवर्तने","m":"quickness in retaliation"},{"d":"गतिवेगम्","m":"speed of arrows"},{"d":"समापन्नौ","m":"happened"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"क्षिपतोश्शरजालानितयोस्तौस्यन्दनोत्तमौ चेरतुस्सम्युगमहीं सासारौ जलदाविव ।","trans":"The network of arrows released by both of them from the chariots were like water streams from two clouds in the battlefield","words":[{"d":"शरजालानि","m":"network of arrows"},{"d":"क्षिपतोः","m":"released"},{"d":"तयोः","m":"by both"},{"d":"स्यन्दनोत्तमौ","m":"excellent warriors"},{"d":"सासारौ","m":"in the battlefield"},{"d":"जलदौइव","m":"like water streams"},{"d":"संयुगमहीम्","m":"like two clouds"},{"d":"चेरतुः","m":"both chariots"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"दर्शयित्वातदातौतुगतिंबहुविधांरणे परस्परस्याभिमुखौपुनरेव च तस्थतुः ।","trans":"Then those two, having seen many movements, once again stood facing each other in the battlefield.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"तौ","m":"those two"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battlefield"},{"d":"बहुविधाम्","m":"many ways"},{"d":"गतिम्","m":"movements"},{"d":"दर्शयित्वा","m":"having seen"},{"d":"पुनरेव","m":"once again"},{"d":"परस्परस्य","m":"one another"},{"d":"अभिमुखौ","m":"facing each other"},{"d":"तस्थतुः","m":"stood"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"धुरंधुरेणरथयोर्वक्त्रंवक्त्रेणवाजिनाम् पताकाश्चपताकाभिस्समीयुस्स्थितयोस्तदा ।","trans":"The two chariots stood facing each other on the battlefield once more, the axle of one chariot facing the axle of another chariot, the flag of one with another flag, the standard with another standard, the face of one horse with the face of another horse stood and it seemed as though they were together.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"स्थितयोः","m":"standing"},{"d":"रथयोः","m":"chariots"},{"d":"धुरम्","m":"axle"},{"d":"धुरेण","m":"with axle"},{"d":"वाजिनाम्","m":"horses"},{"d":"वक्त्रम्","m":"standard"},{"d":"वक्त्रेण","m":"with face"},{"d":"पताकाः","m":"flags"},{"d":"पताकाभिः च","m":"with flag"},{"d":"समीयुः","m":"stood together"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"रावणस्यततोरामोधनुर्मुस्तैश्शितैश्शरैः चतुर्भिश्चतुरोदीप्तान्हयान्प्रत्यपसर्पयत् ।","trans":"Thereupon, Rama, stretching the bow, released four sharp glowing arrows at Ravana's four horses and drove them back.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"there upon"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"धनुर्मुस्तै:","m":"stretching the bow"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"at Ravana"},{"d":"दीप्तान्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"चतुरः","m":"four"},{"d":"हयान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"प्रत्यसर्पयत्","m":"drove back"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"सक्रोधवशमापन्नोहयानामपसर्पणे मुमोचनिशितान्बाणान्राघवायदशाननः ।","trans":"Fallen prey to anger for retreating the horses, the ten headed Ravana released pointed arrows on Raghava.","words":[{"d":"हयानाम्","m":"the horses"},{"d":"अपसर्पणे","m":"retreating"},{"d":"क्रोधवशम्","m":"prey to anger"},{"d":"राघवाय","m":"on Raghava"},{"d":"निशितान्","m":"pointed"},{"d":"बाणान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"मुमोच","m":"released"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"सोतिविद्धोबलवतादशग्रीवेणराघवः जगाम न विकारं च न चापिव्यथितोऽभवत् ।","trans":"Raghava, though wounded by the mighty Ravana's arrows, did notexperience suffering or agitation, nor disquiet.","words":[{"d":"बलवता","m":"mighty"},{"d":"दशग्रीवेण","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"अतिविद्धः","m":"wounded very much"},{"d":"विकारम्","m":"agitated"},{"d":"न जगाम","m":"nor disquieted"},{"d":"व्यथितः च","m":"suffering"},{"d":"न अभवत्","m":"not experienced"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"चिक्षेप च पुनर्भाणान्वज्रपातसमस्वनान् सारथिंवज्रहस्तस्यसमुद्दिश्यदशाननः ।","trans":"The ten headed Ravana with his thunderbolt like hands hurled arrows and struck the charioteer of Rama, making sounds like thunder.","words":[{"d":"दशाननः","m":"Ten headed"},{"d":"वज्रहस्तस्य","m":"with thunderbolt like hands"},{"d":"सारथिम्","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"उद्दिश्य","m":"aimed"},{"d":"वज्रपातसमस्वनान्","m":"equal to thunder"},{"d":"बाणान्","m":"arrow"},{"d":"चिक्षेप","m":"struck"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"मातलेस्तुमहावेगाश्शरीरेपतिताश्शराः न सूक्ष्ममपिसम्मोहंव्यथांवाप्रददुर्युधि ।","trans":"Even though the arrows fell on Matali's body at great speed, he did not feel perturbed or experience even slight suffering.","words":[{"d":"शरीरे","m":"body"},{"d":"पतिताः","m":"fallen"},{"d":"महावेगाः","m":"at great speed"},{"d":"शराः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"सुसूक्ष्ममपि","m":"even slight"},{"d":"सम्बोहम्","m":"perturbance"},{"d":"व्यथांवा","m":"or suffering"},{"d":"न प्रददुः","m":"not felt"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तयाधर्षणयाक्रुद्धोमातलेर्नतथात्मनः चकारशरजालेनराघवोविमुखंरिपुम् ।","trans":"Rama was furious for tormenting Matali like that, but not for hurting him and in fury discharged a network of arrows on him (Ravana) and diverted him.","words":[{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"मातलेः","m":"Matali"},{"d":"तयाधर्षणया","m":"like that torment"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"furious"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"himself"},{"d":"तथा","m":"in that way"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"शरजालेन","m":"by the network of arrows"},{"d":"रिपुम्","m":"enemy"},{"d":"विमुखम्","m":"diverted"},{"d":"चकार","m":"made"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"विंशतिंत्रिंशतिंषष्टिंशतशोऽथसहस्रशः मुमोचराघवोवीरस्सायकान्स्यन्दनेरिपोः ।","trans":"Heroic Raghava thereafter, let loose shafts in twenties, thirties, sixties, hundreds, and thousands at Ravana's chest.","words":[{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"स्यन्दने","m":"chest"},{"d":"विंशतिम्","m":"twenty"},{"d":"त्रिंशतिम्","m":"thirty"},{"d":"षष्टिम्","m":"sixty"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"शतशः","m":"hundreds"},{"d":"सहस्रशः","m":"thousands"},{"d":"सायकान्","m":"shafts"},{"d":"मुमोच","m":"loosed at him"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"रावणोऽपिततःक्रुद्धोरथस्थराक्षसेश्वरः गदामुसलवर्षेणरामंप्रत्यर्दयद्रणे ।","trans":"Enraged Ravana, the king of Rakshasas, also in return, retaliated with maces and mallets.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"enraged"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणोऽपि","m":"Ravana also"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in the battle"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"गदामुसलवर्षेण","m":"with mace and mallets"},{"d":"प्रत्यर्थयत्","m":"in return"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"तत्प्रवृतंपुनर्युद्धंतुमुलंरोमहर्षणम् गदानांमुसलानां च परिघाणांचनिस्स्वनैः ।शराणांपुङ्खवातैश्चक्षुभितास्सप्तसागराः","trans":"Once again ensued a tumultuous war fought with maces, mallets, and iron bars, caused hair to stand and the resound of the speed of weapons caused agitation in the seven seas.","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"प्रवृतं","m":"ensued"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"तुमुलम्","m":"tumultuous"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"caused hair to stand"},{"d":"गदानाम्","m":"with maces"},{"d":"मुसलानां च","m":"and mallets"},{"d":"परिघाणां च","m":"iron bars"},{"d":"निःस्वनैः","m":"by the resound of speed"},{"d":"सप्तसागराः","m":"the seven seas"},{"d":"क्षुभिताः","m":"agitated"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"तत्प्रवृतंपुनर्युद्धंतुमुलंरोमहर्षणम् गदानांमुसलानां च परिघाणांचनिस्स्वनैः ।शराणांपुङ्खवातैश्चक्षुभितास्सप्तसागराः","trans":"Once again ensued a tumultuous war fought with maces, mallets, and iron bars, caused hair to stand and the resound of the speed of weapons caused agitation in the seven seas.","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"प्रवृतं","m":"ensued"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"तुमुलम्","m":"tumultuous"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"caused hair to stand"},{"d":"गदानाम्","m":"with maces"},{"d":"मुसलानां च","m":"and mallets"},{"d":"परिघाणां च","m":"iron bars"},{"d":"निःस्वनैः","m":"by the resound of speed"},{"d":"सप्तसागराः","m":"the seven seas"},{"d":"क्षुभिताः","m":"agitated"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"क्षुब्दानांसागराणां च पातालतलवासिनः ।व्यथितादानवाःसर्वेपन्नगाश्चसहस्रशः","trans":"By the agitation and sounds in the seas, all the Danavas and snakes in thousands inhabiting the seas got distressed.","words":[{"d":"क्षुब्दानाम्","m":"sounds"},{"d":"सागराणाम्","m":"in the seas"},{"d":"पातालतलवासिनः","m":"inhabiting the subterranean region"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"पन्नगाश्च","m":"snakes"},{"d":"व्यथिताः","m":"distressed"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"चकम्पेमेदिनीकृत्स्नासशैलवनकानना ।भास्करोनिष्प्रभश्चासीन्नवनौचापिमारुतः","trans":"The entire globe with its mountains, gardens and forests shook, the Sun lost his radiance, even the wind did not blow.","words":[{"d":"सशैलवनकानना","m":"with mountains, gardens, forests"},{"d":"कृत्स्ना","m":"dark"},{"d":"मेदिनी","m":"earth"},{"d":"चकम्पे","m":"shook"},{"d":"भास्करश्च","m":"even the sun"},{"d":"निष्प्रभः","m":"lost radiance"},{"d":"आसीत्","m":"not move"},{"d":"मारुतश्चापि","m":"even the wind"},{"d":"न ववौ","m":"not blow"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"ततोदेवास्सगन्धर्वास्सिद्धाश्चपरमर्षयः ।चिन्तामापेदिरेसर्वेसकिन्नरमहोरगाः","trans":"Thereafter, the Gandharvas, Devas, Siddhas, great sages, Kinneras and huge serpents all of them became anxious.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सगन्धर्वाः","m":"the Gandharvas"},{"d":"सिद्धाश्च","m":"Siddhas"},{"d":"परमर्षयः","m":"great sages"},{"d":"सकिन्नरमहोरगाः","m":"Kinneras, and huge serpents"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"चिन्ताम्","m":"anxiety"},{"d":"अपेदिरे","m":"became"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"स्वस्तिगोब्राह्मणेभ्योऽस्तुलोकास्तिष्ठन्तुशाश्वताः ।जयतांराघयसङ्ख्येरावणंराक्षसेश्वरम् एवंजपन्तोऽपश्यंस्तेदेवास्सर्षिगणास्तदा ।रामरावणयोर्युद्धंसुघोरंरोमहर्षणम्","trans":"\"May the hosts of sages, Devas, cows and brahmanas be auspicious. May all the worlds endure forever. May Rama conquer Ravana, the Rakshasa king,\" chanting in that manner all witnessed the terrific war between Rama and Ravana that caused hair to stand.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"सर्षिगणाः","m":"hosts of sages"},{"d":"ते","m":"the"},{"d":"देवाः","m":"Devas"},{"d":"गोब्राह्मणेभ्यः","m":"cows, brahmanas"},{"d":"स्वस्ति","m":"be auspicious"},{"d":"अस्तु","m":"be"},{"d":"लोकाः","m":"worlds"},{"d":"शाश्वताः","m":"ever"},{"d":"तिष्ठन्तु","m":"endure"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"संख्ये","m":"large numbers"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरम्","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"जयताम्","m":"conquer"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"जपन्तः","m":"chanted"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"caused hair to stand"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"both Rama and Ravana"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"अपश्यन्","m":"witnessed"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"स्वस्तिगोब्राह्मणेभ्योऽस्तुलोकास्तिष्ठन्तुशाश्वताः ।जयतांराघयसङ्ख्येरावणंराक्षसेश्वरम् एवंजपन्तोऽपश्यंस्तेदेवास्सर्षिगणास्तदा ।रामरावणयोर्युद्धंसुघोरंरोमहर्षणम्","trans":"\"May the hosts of sages, Devas, cows and brahmanas be auspicious. May all the worlds endure forever. May Rama conquer Ravana, the Rakshasa king,\" chanting in that manner all witnessed the terrific war between Rama and Ravana that caused hair to stand.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"सर्षिगणाः","m":"hosts of sages"},{"d":"ते","m":"the"},{"d":"देवाः","m":"Devas"},{"d":"गोब्राह्मणेभ्यः","m":"cows, brahmanas"},{"d":"स्वस्ति","m":"be auspicious"},{"d":"अस्तु","m":"be"},{"d":"लोकाः","m":"worlds"},{"d":"शाश्वताः","m":"ever"},{"d":"तिष्ठन्तु","m":"endure"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"संख्ये","m":"large numbers"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरम्","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"जयताम्","m":"conquer"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"जपन्तः","m":"chanted"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"caused hair to stand"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"both Rama and Ravana"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"अपश्यन्","m":"witnessed"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"गन्धर्वाप्सरसांसङ्घादृष्टवायुद्धमनूपमम् ।गगनंगगनाकारंसागरस्सागरोपमः रामरावणयोर्युद्धंरामरावणयोरिव ।एवंब्रुवन्तोददृशुस्तद्युद्धंरामरावणम्","trans":"Gandharvas and Apsaras watching the combination of Rama and Ravana fighting an unimaginable war said that sky is its own analogue for sky, sea is its own analogue to sea, in the same way is the struggle between Rama and Ravana is unique like Rama and Ravana's struggle and looked at the combat.","words":[{"d":"गन्धर्वाप्सरसाम्","m":"Gandharvas and Apsaras"},{"d":"सङ्घाः","m":"combination"},{"d":"अनूपमम्","m":"unimaginable"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"watching"},{"d":"गगनम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"गगनाकारम्","m":"sky is its own analogue"},{"d":"गरोपमः","m":"sea is its own compeer"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"both Rama and Ravana"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"fight"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"likened Rama and Ravana's struggle"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"combat"},{"d":"रामरावणयोरिव"